From tervio TERVI MARKO J Subject Re switzerland at In article writes does anybody know if this WC is the qualification tournement for the olympic games ' in Lillehammer or are some teams already qualified for hopp schwiiz daniel The top teams of this tournament will play in the Olympics next The last team of this tournament top two of pool B Great Britain and Poland and the winner of pool C Latvia will play for the last Olympic spot next However if next year's hosts Norway were to finish which would be no surprise then it's the team of pool A that will have to play in the qualification Marko Tervio